summary: When The Choirs Sing in Harmony
title: When The Choirs Sing in Harmony
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2K7JmNX

by Solaris_Breeze

In heaven, there are nine choirs, each with their own duty to protect Earth, keep balance in Heaven and stop the demons from Hell attacking their Lord.

Namjoon, one of the best Dominions, in an attempt to save his precious friend, almost falls to Hell and is lost. One of his close friends, Seokjin, one of the best Seraphims, saves him from being lost to Hell.

Can these two over come their choir duties, stereotypes and their emotions and come together at the end?
